Name: Placerville, California, USA
Details/Description: Proud Boys flash ok symbol in racist hoodies, ignore the toy drive's COVID guidelines by congregating in close proximity on foot.  Placerville's mayor states the group's presence makes it uncomfortable for tourists and businesses,  condemns the group's presence and ganglike behavior. Local police condemn the Proud Boys for using the Toys for Tots event to push a political agenda.
Note: Hangtown was Placerville's original name. Racial symbols i.e. the noose, were seen on Proud Boys attire.

Form of Incident: Terrorist Attack,Protest,Foiled Terrorist Attack,Bomb,Arrest,Election Interference,Attempted Coup,Disruption of Political Institution
Details/Description: A series of events in Washington DC including storming of the capitol by right wing militias disrupting the Congressional certification of the electoral college votes. Calls for hanging VP Mike Pence have been heard. Shots have been fired inside the chamber. The National Guard has been activated on request from the Mayor of DC.
